data.description: PRICE REDUCED FOR A QUICK SALE! This home is even more impressive with FRESH interior paint. With all the storms that have hit Florida over the past 10 years alone, this house has NEVER flooded. Talk about peace of mind with your future home. Are you dreaming of a waterfront haven that's just a 15-minute cruise from the Gulf of Mexico? Dive into a home that's got updates galore and is waiting for someone like you to make memories in.  First off, this beauty stands on one and a half lots, with a partially fenced in with a sturdy 4' chain link. Much larger than the neighbors! Stroll out to 90ft of riprap safeguarding that seawall integrity, and imagine the countless sunsets you'd witness from the floating dock or from the additional large dock that is partially covered.  Feel the summer vibes with an above-ground pool, spacious and perfect for those lazy afternoons. Got a boat? A Remote controlled 10,000 LB BOAT LIFT was added in 2017. That’s for your convenience. And if you’re all about the relaxation, that hot tub is calling your name. The two-car garage is a dream, but wait till you see the adjoining man-cave! Whether it's hobbies, projects, or just some downtime, this space is golden.    Now, let's talk updates: from the hurricane shutters with a transferable lifetime warranty to the modern electrical system, and from the leaf filter system in gutters to the updated sewer lines (2021), every inch of this home has been thoughtfully maintained. Comfort? The central A/C new sensor, drain maintained and cleaned has got you covered. Even the water heater has been updated! It is rare to have a such a well maintained home that needs very little.   Step inside, and you'll love the new laminate tile flooring throughout. The kitchen boasts updated appliances, and the bathroom? Freshly updated for your comfort.  Other perks include double-paned windows for energy efficiency, a negative termite inspection ensuring peace of mind, and all appliances, even that extra fridge in the garage, are part of the package.  This beautiful 2 bedroom and 2 bath home has plenty of flexible space to be customized as you wish.    In a nutshell? 12620 3rd Isle is more than a home; it’s a lifestyle. Ready to dive into waterfront living? The door's open! Leisure Beach is not actually a beach, instead, it is the southernmost waterfront neighborhood in Hudson. Its canals are a little wider than most of the other neighborhoods, and newer as well. They were dug by a developer about 10 years after the rest of Hudson was.
